description: Lists one or more Amazon Q Business Web Experiences.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The identifier of the Amazon Q Business application linked to the listed web experiences.

nested_items.name: webExperiences
nested_items.description: An array of summary information for one or more Amazon Q Business experiences.

nested_items.name: webExperienceId
nested_items.description: The identifier of your Amazon Q Business web experience.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp when the Amazon Q Business application was last updated.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The Unix timestamp when your Amazon Q Business web experience was updated.

nested_items.name: defaultEndpoint
nested_items.description: The endpoint URLs for your Amazon Q Business web experience. The URLs are unique and fully hosted by Amazon Web Services.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of your Amazon Q Business web experience.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, Amazon Q Business returns this token, which you can use in a later request to list the next set of messages.
